  "about": {
    "url": "https://maddphotography.mypixieset.com/about-me/",
    "title": "about me - maddphotography",
    "text": "HOME\nINFO\nGET TO KNOW ME\nLOREM IPSUM DOLOR SIT AMET\nPhotography Is Poetry\nWelcome to Madd Photography\n\n\n\n\nWelcome to my page! My name is Madeleine + I am a Psychology major with a minor in business at Abilene Christian University. I was born and raised in El Paso, TX, but have resided in the DFW area.\n\n\n\n\nI found myself with a passion for photography when I attended a workshop held by Asia Joy, Owner of Photo By Joy. All it took was one workshop and I was hooked. I was constantly craving more information and wanted to learn everything I could. After four years of attending photography workshops I finally invested in myself and purchased my own camera and then begun Madd Photography.\n\nHobbies\n\n\n\n\nPhotography is something I enjoy with every ounce of my being, but it is not all to me. I love working out and talking about love languages. I love discovering new music and having dance parties. Some of my favorite artists are Faye Webster, Weezer, SZA, Bad Bunny + Harry Styles. \n\nPhotography Style\n\n\n\n\nI am all about being in the moment. I try to guide you, but not pose you. Most people have the fear of looking awkward in pictures because of prior photography experiences. I am here to have fun and make you look GOOD. \n\nWant To Work Together?\nCONTACT ME\n@MADDPHOTOGRAPHY__\nHOME\nINFO\nGET TO KNOW ME\n \n\n© 2026 maddphotography",
